description:
Priced to rent quickly. Non-smoking, responsible, and caring prospect(s) only. Lease term is highly flexible. More new updated photos are coming. Designed for luxury living is this 4 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath 4-story row house (with 2262 square feet) in East Falls. Steps to the SEPTA (inter-region metro rail transit system) "East Falls" train station of the Norristown Line (which takes you to downtown Philly in just 20 minutes). Proximity to the bustling Kelly drive, historic Manayunk, and the scenic Fairmount Park. So this house is ideal for commuters, cyclists, and runners preferring large spaces with modern state-of-art amenities. Close to Drexel Med, Temple, PCOM and Philadelphia Univ.
The beautifully finished basement, which has its own private full bathroom is spacious in being over 540 square feet, and can function either as a BIG 4th bedroom suite, or as a play/family room, both of 420 square footage of space with own big window;
The biggest technology-based feature inside this house is its dual (two) new modern full-size central-air HVAC systems each with its own respective thermostat - which is distinct from the MUCH cheaper but MUCH less effective conventional approach of having one central air and one or two add-on mini-splits to cover four stories of spaces - which renders all four stories of this house never needing to worry about enough heating and cooling in summer and winter (a feature which sets this house apart from other 4-story similar houses).
lease term is HIGHLY flexible; short term lease is available with higher monthly rent; requires first month, last month, and security deposit (equaling one month's rent), to move in; tenants pay water/sewer, electric, gas, and Verizon high-speed Internet; will conduct tenant screening (on things like credit score, background, rental history).
Pet(s) is/are allowed for long term lease. Pet(s) is/are not allowed for short term leases.
Other amenities include:
- driveway long enough to park two vehicles back to back off-street.
- full size washer and dryer in-unit;
- Modern full kitchen with beautiful cabinets, granite countertops and island, and a spacious dining area;
- a beautiful fireplace in the living room;
- modern 3-feet wide big tall refrigerator with humidity-controlled Crisper drawer (ideal for maintaining freshness);
- Bosch brand state-of-art dishwasher;
- Samsung brand state-of-art gas range with air-frying function;
- beautiful hardwood flooring throughout;
- plenty of closet spaces, including a 44-inch wide pantry closet;
- a decent-size storage room in the basement;
- big deck in the back of the house, ideal for outdoor summer BBQ and gatherings;
- additional (second) big fridge (with freezer section) in the basement for extra refrigerated and frozen storage of additional food and beverages;
- provision of a decent-size shed for additional storage (of, e.g., bikes) as needed at the front of house;
